---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="House rules & stay instructions" description="House rules and practical instructions for guests at Villa Sancti Albani.">
	<div class="content content--narrow">
		<h1>House rules &amp; stay instructions</h1>
		<p class="lede">Please treat the house and land as you would a friend&apos;s quiet retreat. Adjust every bullet below to match your final operations.</p>

		<h2>Arrival &amp; departure</h2>
		<ul class="list-plain">
			<li>Check-in after [time]. Check-out by [time].</li>
			<li>Lock doors and close windows when you leave for the day.</li>
			<li>Thermostat, fireplace, and woodstove notes: [add instructions].</li>
		</ul>

		<h2>Indoors</h2>
		<ul class="list-plain">
			<li>No shoes on [specify rooms] if that is your preference.</li>
			<li>Please use coasters on wood surfaces.</li>
			<li>Kitchen: [dishwasher, trash, recycling, compost].</li>
		</ul>

		<h2>Outdoors</h2>
		<ul class="list-plain">
			<li>Fire pit only when permitted; extinguish fully before bed.</li>
			<li>Respect property boundaries and neighboring driveways.</li>
		</ul>

		<h2>Quiet &amp; neighbors</h2>
		<p>Outdoor quiet hours from [time] to [time]. This is a residential woodland setting, not a party venue.</p>

		<h2>Pets</h2>
		<p>[Allowed / not allowed / case-by-case with fee and crate rules.]</p>

		<h2>Smoking</h2>
		<p>[No smoking indoors / designated outdoor area only.]</p>

		<h2>Trash &amp; departure checklist</h2>
		<ul class="list-plain">
			<li>Strip used beds; start towels in [laundry location].</li>
			<li>Remove perishables; wipe spills.</li>
			<li>Trash to [shed / totes / haul policy].</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
</BaseLayout>
